data.description: Single level living in this well cared for 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom townhome with attached garage.  Convenient Columbia Falls location just minutes from downtown and all services.  Exterior features a fenced backyard for privacy and/or pets, underground irrigation, storage shed and backyard patio.  The home interior has a warm cozy feel with a lovely living room electric fireplace that provides efficient heat in the fall & winter months.  All new kitchen appliances, new water heater and new washer & dryer too!  Custom built-in shelving in guest bedroom #1 makes for a wonderful home office.  Only 18 miles to Glacier National Park and 17 miles to the North Kalispell shopping hub.  Call Shelby Nash Hunter 406.253.0222 or Kelly Gerhart 406.253.4856 or your real estate professional.
